messages.message: the rotation of this doc upon upload was jarring to me. also seems like the image quality decreased quite a bit
What do you find jarring, @Natasha? What would it make less so, and still help you with overall experience in Converse app?

I wasn't expecting it to be rotated + all the black space + the top and bottom left of the document getting cut off. I wasn't expecting the document to look any different from the original file.

Also, this sample doc when uploaded in a pdf combined with the other sample docs did not get rotated, but uploaded on its own it did
